text: Large and lovely Park Village home with lots of updates! Updated kitchen with new countertops and large 2 door pantry. Large living, dining rooms and family room area that opens up to new deck to enjoy the sunshine. Both bedrooms have updated bathrooms and large walk in shower off primary. Even more updates with new roof and windows, new paint throughout, new lighting, doors and deck sliders, plus new decks and low maintenance landscaping. Tankless gas water heater and heatpump for comfortable living. Nice storage/shop plus garden shed. This homes neat and tidy landscaped back area opens up to a large and grassy green belt great for walking Rover or Sparky! Truly a must see!

Charming Country Home...2 bedrooms, 1 bath, spacious kitchen with gas range, dishwasher, refrigerator, lots of counter space. Living room with beautiful westerly views & sunsets. New septic & drain field in 2020, new Visqueen and insulation in crawlspace. Fully fenced yard with detached 2 door garage, works great for 1 car and shop space. Could be modified for 2 cars. Convenient to I-5 and minutes to town.

Your new Pied--terre! A totally remodeled 1930s bungalow just steps from the beaches of Anacortes Washington Park. A private water view deck out front w/ French doors. Inside, cathedral ceilings & plank flooring in great room w/tiled fireplace surround, kitchen w/eating space & new lighting, a new fridge & dishwasher. A unique tapestry room divider, bath w/new tiled-in shower, laundry & walk-in closet space. Outside, surrounded by a private fenced-in patio, new landscaping & lighting in the terraced gardens & greenhouse, a fun sidewalk fire-pit next to a custom concrete driveway. Simply remarkable & charming beyond belief. You can walk to the Washington State ferry for a trip to the San Juans. Next door MLS 2244567 4 sale.

Welcome to your new home, a sanctuary designed to reflect your elevated lifestyle. Nestled in the Summer Ridge neighborhood, this timeless residence reflects both elegance and modern sophistication. An airy and inviting atmosphere will welcome you home, where the soft ambiance invites relaxation & intimate gatherings. The kitchen is equipped to meet every culinary need with style and ease and is where cherished memories are made. Indulge in the newly remodeled bathrooms which boast both modern design and ultimate relaxation. W/ every detail impeccably curated, you'll realize this is the home you've been waiting for. A large .67 acre lot, fully fenced-in backyard, RV parking, wood floors & central A/C make this home, absolute perfection.

Welcome to this charming Anacortes home, ideally located just a block away from Volunteer-Kiwanis Meadow Park and a few minutes to downtown. This one-level living gem features a delightful front deck, a covered back patio, and a cozy sunroom. The backyard is a gardener's paradise, boasting beautiful flowers, fruit trees, and a greenhouse. This home also includes a huge bedroom or bonus room with a private entrance, perfect for flex space or a caretaker's bedroom. The driveway is big enough to park a small RV or boat. Conveniently located with easy access to Highway 20, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and accessibility.

They don't make them like this anymore! Tucked away on a quiet cul-de-sac, this private and spacious 3BR, 2BA rambler has a mid century modern vibe with a newer roof, furnace, exterior paint and kitchen counters & floors. You will love the huge, partially fenced yard with lovely, mature landscaping and multiple sheds/outbuildings for plenty of storage and/or hobbies. Enjoy both charm and utility with features such as a picturesque bay window in the oversized living room, large primary suite with attached bath and separate vanity nook, separate den/office/sun room off the dining room and much more. With a 2-car garage plus extra/RV parking, this property has it all!

Charming, bright Mount Vernon mid-century rambler with beautiful original hardwood floors throughout, fresh interior paint, & stone surround wood burning fireplace! Kitchen features a moveable island for additional counter space & storage as well as a freestanding dishwasher. Large storage closets can be found throughout the home as well as in the full bathroom which also features a double sink, shower, & tub. Spend time sitting on your front deck or go out the back sliding glass door off the dining area to the welcoming fully fenced backyard with mature landscaping and both deck & patio for lounging and entertaining! Attached one car garage with storage, work space, and shop sink. Additional parking available alongside the garage as well!

Room for everyone in this enchanting 3 bedroom 2 bath home at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac in a natural wooded setting with hanging gardens. Great-room concept on main level includes a sunken music room for private recitals. The enormous garage with shop on lower level, wrap around deck with ramp to the main living level. And penthouse bedroom on upper level make this a must see property!. Walking distance to your own private Marthas beach, pools, tennis and sports courts, play field and golf course, boat moorage (if available). ;

Welcome home to the desirable neighborhood of Skagit Highlands! Enjoy all of the parks and nature trails that surround you. The backyard is a gardeners' oasis. Open floor plan concept for entertaining - The kitchen is a gourmet cooks delight - Including gas stove, large walk in pantry, plenty of counter space and all new appliances. Relax in your fully fenced, private back yard with nature surrounding you. Heat pump will keep you warm in the winter and cool in the summer. First time on market since being built. Lot next door is owned and maintained by HOA -

Welcome to the neighborhood! This wonderful home offers great room living with vaulted ceilings and a gas fireplace. Kitchen with SS appliances, pantry storage and a breakfast bar. Spacious Primary Bedroom with private bath on the main level, plus two additional bedrooms and full bath. Lower-level family room with fireplace and an extra finished room - perfect for a home office/flex space. Updated flooring throughout. Large deck and patio for relaxing or entertaining. Level rear yard with garden space and shed for additional storage. Two car garage. Large driveway affords space for RV parking. Perfectly located in the heart of Mount Vernon, this home offers convenient access to shopping, dining, parks and schools!

Idealy located in the heart of the cherished Edison community, this beautiful craftsman home radiates charm and appeal. Meticulously updated while preserving its magnetic historic charisma, this home embodies the sought-after character of its age and location. The rustic fir flooring throughout adds a unique dimension, emphasizing the home's individuality. An outdoor kitchen, recently installed, enhances the appeal and caters to those who love to entertain. The storybook floor plan includes 3 spacious bedrooms and an open concept main floor with seamless flow, creating an inviting and functional living space. A cozy office with custom built in shelving is just one of many features that set this home apart. A truly unique opportunity.

Nestled on 5.32 Acres, this Rare Waterfront Estate Soaks in Southerly Puget Sound & Territorial Views. 557 of Waterfront Includes Sandy Beach, Bulkhead, Boat Ramp & Two Mooring Buoys. Main Home Features Luxurious Kitchen Offering Quartzite Counters, Large Walk-in Pantry & Opens to Dining Area w/ Wet Bar. Living Room w/ Granite FP & Expansive Windows Allow Remarkable Views Throughout. Private Office w/ Built-ins, Granite FP & Patio Access. Upper Level Offers Two Guest Beds, Guest Bath & Opulent Primary Suite w/ Lrg Walk-in Shower, Soaking Tub, Heated Floors & WIC. Finished Bsmt Includes Rec Room, Bath, Laundry & Workshop. Level-Entry MIL w/ Full Bath & Water Views Above 2-Car Garage. No Ferry Required! Boat House Available, Not Included

Nestled on a secluded acre in Conway, this charming home is surrounded by protected lots, ensuring stunning views. The single-level layout features an open design with vaulted ceilings. The custom kitchen has Thermador appliances, including double ovens, quartz countertops, and a large pantry. The primary bedroom has a walk-in closet and a master bathroom with a luxurious shower and heated tiles. It includes a cozy family room with NanaWall glass folding door bringing the outdoors in. Created for entertainment, the patio showcases an outdoor fire pit. A sizable three-car garage offers ample storage space. This property is an outstanding opportunity to own a home where comfort and convenience converge.

An Anacortes icon on Sunset Avenue, just a stones throw from the beaches of Washington Park. Main-level living throughout, a beautifully refreshed 1940s-era 2bed, 1bath home, fronted by its unique arbor, a south-facing glassed-in deck with peek-a-boo view. Cozy great room w/fireplace & triple-pane windows, dining area, new kitchen w/sit-down bar, deep sink, newly-tiled backsplash, coffee/wine bar & glowing Tiffany lighting. Check out the retro-charmed detached 202sqft apartment with living, kitchen, bath, sleeping loft, skylights. Serene deck w/hot tub & hanging vines right out the back door. Low-maintenance stone landscaping, plus 2 fenced-in decks. Garage/workshop. Stroll to & from San Juan ferry. Next door MLS#2244566 also 4 sale.

Perfectly situated rambler in quiet Brickyard Creek cul-de-sac. Extra generous living room with picturesque bay windows. Living and dining space leads into large kitchen overlooking a family room. Three bedrooms, two baths including a private primary suite at the end of the hall. House comes complete with 2 year new roof, efficient hydronic heating, RV parking, and 94 x 155 outbuilding. Fresh interior paint and stainless steel appliances. Heating system recently fully inspected and serviced. Private backyard with mature landscaping and partially fenced. Close to Sedro amenities, hospital, and downtown shopping.

Experience the perfect blend of rural charm and urban convenience in this lovely 3-bedroom home nestled on the outskirts of town. Enjoy a quaint and welcoming neighborhood atmosphere with a hint of country vibes, while being just outside of city limits. Beyond your backyard, discover the ease of access to I5, with Burlington/Mt Vernon nearby for all your shopping needs. This single-level home is situated on a generous lot surrounded by mature vegetation, providing an escape into county living. Ideal for those craving tranquility without compromising on modern conveniences.

Welcome to Samish Island living! This highly desirable area is home to a vibrant community with a focus on arts, music and peaceful living. The 8, 712 square foot lot is ready for you to create your new home, with slightly sloped views of Samish Bay to the north. This property includes private shared beach access just down the block for launching kayaks and canoes or just a walk on the beach. Amenities on Samish Island include the public beach, Samish Island Park which includes playground, tennis and more. Events include the Samish Island Arts Festival, potlucks, parades and all-island garage sale! And just minutes away from the eccentric town of Edison with great food and festivals, Bayview hiking trails and the beautiful Chuckanut Drive.

A rare opportunity awaits to own your own compound nestled on 20 acres overlooking the Skagit River, with breathtaking views of Sauk Mountain and Mount Baker. The property boasts a variety of fruit trees including apple, cherry, plum, pear, and peach, as well as enchanting Korean spice trees emitting a delightful aroma. The cabin is connected to electricity, and a 700-gallon water catchment system ensures a renewable water source. Featuring three cabins, a cook shack, and a 14x60 storage container for added convenience. Secluded yet conveniently located just 1.5 miles from town, with easy access to schools, shopping, medical facilities, and recreational areas. Situated only 1.25 miles from Lake Shannon. Schedule your private tour today!

Introducing this impeccably maintained & expansive residence nestled in Highland Greens! Step into the welcoming embrace of a three-bedroom, two-and-a-half-bathroom home featuring an open-concept main level leading seamlessly to a delightful patio & fully fenced backyard. The heart of the home boasts a charming kitchen with a walk-in pantry, double oven, quartz countertops, & stainless steel appliances. Upstairs, retreat to the sizable primary bedroom with a walk-in closet & luxurious five-piece bathroom. Additionally, discover two generous bedrooms, a full hall bath, a convenient laundry room, & a versatile bonus room/loft area on the upper level. Stay cool & comfortable with central air conditioning, perfect for the upcoming summer months!

Come see this hidden gem! Conveniently nestled in trees at the end of a dead end street, this nearly half acre lot is secluded, but also steps from a charming, walkable neighborhood, and minutes from the water. Inside you will find vaulted ceilings and an open living space flooded with natural light from ample windows, throughout. A large loft features an on suite bathroom and walk-in closet. A 2nd bedroom and updated bathroom can be found on the main level. In the partially finished basement you will find a 3rd bedroom with a separate outdoor entrance, perfect for an office, guest room, or flex space. Surrounded by nature, the upper deck and lower patio are ready for entertaining. Turn key with brand new roof- 5/24! Come make it your own.

Just under 22 acres and two parcels this forested lot is immersed in nature yet less than 10 minutes to I-5. This lot has endless possibilities. Property backs up to Butler Creek and has a small stream running through. Bring your builder and your imagination to get started on your dream home today.

Step into modern luxury with this like-new gem! You'll love the open layout, seamlessly connecting the spacious living room, dining area & well-appointed kitchen w/a slider opening onto the backyard. The kitchen boasts SS appliances, pantry, quartz counters, center island, & ample counter space for all your cooking needs. Retreat to the generously sized primary suite, flooded w/natural light, & enjoy the spa-like en-suite featuring a double vanity, soaker tub, walk-in shower, & oversized walk-in closet. Each bedroom offers a bright & airy ambiance & plenty of closet space along w/added ease of an upstairs laundry. Savor summer evenings in the privacy of your fully fenced backyard & enjoy the convenience of a full-size 2-car garage.

ASSUMABLE 3.25% VA LOAN! Move in ready daylight basement rambler boasting 2, 118sq.ft. of living space on a spacious .53acre lot. Covered front patio entry leads to foyer entry. Main floor features vaulted great room w/ cozy f/p & slider to rear deck overlooking greenbelt. Quartz kitchen w/ lots of cabinet & counter space & formal dining room. Bedroom & 1/2 bath on main. Fully finished basement features 2nd living room w/ slider to large rear trex deck, primary suite w/ 3/4 bath & oversize closet, additional bedroom w/ full guest bath. Full laundry room w/ soaking sink. Oversize 576sq.ft. garage & driveway parking. Conveniently located w/ quick commute to I5, shopping, dining & schools. Ask about the assumable loan & save on this home!

Looking for quiet country living? Come view this beautiful home nestled on 5 private acres in a parklike setting in desirable Prairie Acres community! This home is 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, 2, 472 sf and offers an open floor plan w/ living room, dining room & family room w/a cozy propane stove. The kitchen features granite counters, an island, eating bar, pantry and tons of storage. There is a flex room/office off the family room with built in cabinetry. The primary bedroom suite is huge & features an ensuite bath & large walk-in closet. Enjoy relaxing on the huge covered deck overlooking the fully fenced backyard. House has A/C & wired for a generator. Detached garage, several outbuildings, covered RV/boat parking too! This one is a must see!

Welcome home to this darling bungalow in Lyman! This charming home isn't built like all those cookie cutter floor plans! Check out the warm and cozy the living room perfect to invite guests in with free standing woodstove, an excellent heat source on a cool PNW evening. Conveniently located near the dining room and living room, this efficient kitchen is complete with oak cabinets, tiled backsplash behind the sink, newer appliances that stay with the home and lots of storage. Each bedroom has a large closet for storage, windows for sunlight and ample space for furniture. The primary suite is complete with a full bath shower combo and big walk-in closet. The large shop is perfect for any home project, storing RV's, boats, car projects & more!

Ideally located 3 bd 2 Bath beautiful spacious newer home with an open floor plan. Walk to parks, restaurants, library, soccer fields front row seats to local events. Home features solar panels lowering utility bill to $8 per month average. Open kitchen large granite island, granite counter tops throughout, Freshly painted decks, 220V in garage/shop. RV parking, 900sq unfinished basement waiting for your touch. Newly finished 230sq ft office/den/under stairs nook. Fruit trees, garden space and additional parking. This home is beautiful and move in ready!
